//git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md\n\n(End of file - total 50 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-001 ŌĆö CRD AgentRuntime ń▒╗Õ×ŗÕ«Üõ╣ē\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-001 ŌĆö CRD AgentRuntime ń▒╗Õ×ŗÕ«Üõ╣ē |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\nÕ«Üõ╣ē AgentRuntime CRD ńÜä Go ń▒╗Õ×ŗń╗ōµ×ä’╝īÕīģµŗ¼:\n- `AgentRuntime` ń▒╗Õ×ŗÕÅŖÕģČ `Spec`ŃĆü`Status`\n- `AgentRuntimeList` ń▒╗Õ×ŗ\n- `CodeInterpreter` ń▒╗Õ×ŗÕÅŖÕģČ `Spec`ŃĆü`Status`\n- `CodeInterpreterList` ń▒╗Õ×ŗ\n- ńøĖÕģ│ÕĖĖķćÅŃĆüµĀćńŁŠŃĆüµ│©Ķ¦ŻÕ«Üõ╣ē","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md","time":{"start":1775838770259,"end":1775838770281}}}}
